-- BMG Names Hermann Chief Executive Officer, Estado Says
-- B y   N e y   H a y a s h i
-- 2012-11-24T17:41:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-24/bmg-names-antonio-hermann-chief-executive-officer-estado-says.html
Brazilian lender Banco BMG SA named
Antonio Hermann its chief executive officer, replacing Ricardo Guimaraes, O Estado de S.Paulo reported, without saying where it
got the information.  BMG also named Alcides Tapias its chairman, O Estado said.  A press official for BMG declined to comment on the report
when contacted by Bloomberg News.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ney Hayashi in Sao Paulo at 
 ncruz4@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
